						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Loss 4 -->
				<div class="loss-item flex items-start space-x-3 sm:space-x-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-3 sm:p-4 shadow-md border border-red-100 animate-fadeInUp delay-400">
					<div class="flex-shrink-0">
						<div class="w-8 h-8 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-red-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
							<svg class="w-4 h-4 sm:w-5 sm:h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
							</svg>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
						<p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
							<span class="font-bold text-red-600">Semakin jauh</span> dari impian umroh yang Anda idamkan
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Loss 5 -->
				<div class="loss-item flex items-start space-x-3 sm:space-x-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-3 sm:p-4 shadow-md border border-red-100 animate-fadeInUp delay-500">
					<div class="flex-shrink-0">
